Insider Activity


Individual




Raymond D. Smoot



Dr. Raymond D. Smoot, Jr. PhD, is Chairman at Union Bankshares Corp., Independent Director at RGC Resources, Inc., and Secretary at Virginia Tech Intellectual Properties, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at RGC Resources, Inc., Carilion Clinic, and Virginia Tech Corporate Research Center, Inc.
Dr. Smoot was previously employed as Chairman by StellarOne Bank, Chairman by StellarOne Corp., Chairman by First National Bank of Clifton Forge, Chief Executive Officer, Secretary & Treasurer by Virginia Tech Foundation, Inc., and Treasurer & Vice President-Administration by Virginia Polytechnic Institute & State University. He also served on the board at FNB Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Virginia Polytechnic Institute & State University, a graduate degree from Virginia Polytechnic Institute & State University, and a doctorate degree from The Ohio State University.



