Raymond D. Smoot Jr., Ph.D.: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 6:39 AM ET
Diversified Financial Services

Company Overview of Virginia Tech Foundation Incorporated



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Raymond D. Smoot Jr., Ph.D.Chief Operating Officer, Secretary and Treasurer, Virginia Tech Foundation IncorporatedAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 6 Board Members in 6 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships70--
Background

		Dr. Raymond D. Smoot, Jr., also known as Ray, Ph.D. serves as the Chief Operating Officer, Secretary and Treasurer at Virginia Tech Foundation Incorporated. Dr. Smoot has financial, investment and real estate development experience. He served as a Vice President for Administration and Treasurer at Virginia Tech from 1998 to 2003. Dr. Smoot has been the Chairman of StellarOne Corporation since March 1, 2010; Union First Market Bankshares Corporation since January 1, 2014 ... and Union Bankshares Corporation since January 1, 2014. He serves as the Chairman of the Virginia Tech Corporate Research Center. He has been the Chairman of the Board and Director at Union Bank & Trust since January 2014. He served as Chairman of Arbor DR BR (formerly StellarOne Bank). He serves as Director of Carilion Clinic Inc. Dr. Smoot has been a Director of RGC Resources, Inc. since January 2005. Dr. Smoot has been an Independent Director at Union Bankshares Corporation since January 1, 2014. He serves as a Director of Virginia Tech Intellectual Properties, Inc. He has been a Director of StellarOne Corporation since 1998. Dr. Smoot served as a Director of FNB Corp. since February 2004. Dr. Smoot holds an MS from Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University; BA from Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University and PhD from The Ohio State University.Read Full Background




